headline: Akamai Technologies (AKAM) Stock Jumps 4.7%: Will It Continue to Soar?
summary: Akamai Technologies (AKAM) witnessed a jump in share price last session on above-average trading volume. The latest trend in earnings estimate revisions for the stock doesn't suggest further strength down the road.
